When should I wash my hands?
As often as possible, but especially: • Before touching your face (eyes, mouth, nose); • After coughing, sneezing or blowing your nose; • After going to the bathroom; • When your hands are visibly dirty or after touching something dirty;
How often should one sterilize hands?

